WEBVTT

00:03.089 --> 00:05.040
Oh, God, oh, God, an activist.

00:05.167 --> 00:07.100
Quick,
pretend we're on the phone.

00:07.136 --> 00:08.969
Uh-huh, uh-huh, uh-huh.
Uh-huh, uh-huh.

00:09.004 --> 00:10.804
Uh-huh, uh-huh. Sorry. We're
pretending to be on the phone.

00:10.839 --> 00:11.805
Tough spot.

00:11.840 --> 00:13.206
I was here last week

00:13.242 --> 00:15.008
trying to organize a cleanup
for garbage island,

00:15.043 --> 00:16.877
and I couldn't even get
a page of signatures.

00:16.912 --> 00:18.512
Really?

00:18.547 --> 00:20.046
I had to go inside
and buy a second clipboard,

00:20.082 --> 00:21.782
I got so many signatures.

00:21.817 --> 00:24.017
You must really have
a noble cause.

00:24.052 --> 00:26.653
I do.
It's called Bad Animals.

00:26.688 --> 00:29.089
Oh, I hate it when people
treat animals badly.

00:29.124 --> 00:31.353
No, there's some really terrible
animals out there.

00:31.456 --> 00:34.824
Just last week, some elephant
tried to attack a poacher.

00:34.859 --> 00:36.392
Bad elephant!

00:36.427 --> 00:38.394
What?!
You can't be serious.

00:38.429 --> 00:40.796
She sounds serious.
I'd like to hear more!

00:40.832 --> 00:42.665
I don't have to hear more!

00:42.700 --> 00:45.368
I'll sign whatever you got,
beautiful.

00:45.403 --> 00:47.303
[ Sniffs ]

00:47.338 --> 00:48.504
Hey, why don't we line up
on <i> that</i> side for the petitions,

00:48.540 --> 00:50.239
and behind <i> me</i> to touch the hair.

00:50.275 --> 00:51.274
[ Sniffs ]

00:52.877 --> 00:54.443
[ Scoffs ]
I can't believe this.

00:54.479 --> 00:56.345
Pick a line, buddy!

00:58.950 --> 01:01.517
♪ Good morning, U.S.A. ♪

01:01.553 --> 01:05.388
♪ I got a feelin' that
it's gonna be a wonderful day ♪

01:05.423 --> 01:08.524
♪ the sun in the sky
has a smile on his face ♪

01:08.560 --> 01:12.795
♪ and he's shinin' a salute
to the American race ♪

01:14.699 --> 01:18.267
♪ Oh, boy, it's swell to say ♪

01:18.303 --> 01:20.536
♪ Good -- ♪
♪ Good morning, U.S.A. ♪

01:20.572 --> 01:26.375
<font color="#ec14bd">Sync & corrections by honeybunny</font>
